snippet.title: Amber Heard Speaks On Being Fired From Aquaman 2...!?
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Speaks On Being Fired From Aquaman 2...!?
In the realm of the DC Comics universe there is a lot going on. And not exactly in the best of ways at times. Because while it's true that the critically-acclaimed film The Suicide Squad has released in theaters to a lot of buzz, there are certain other DC Comics films that have certain controversies going into them. Not the least of which is Aquaman and The Lost Kingdom. Why is so controversial? Because Amber Heard is still in it, and a LOT of fans aren't happy about it...at all. Not that Warner Bros cares apparently. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you go, everyone! A look at the situation with Amber Heard and the second Aquaman film and how Warner Bros isn't taking the fans concerns seriously. Are you surprised by their lack of caring o the matter? Do you think that this proves the dangerous thinking that goes on with certain parts of filmmaking? What do you think will happen next with the court case of Heard and Johnny Depp? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
